Name:           Earth Element
Short Name:     earth
Level Required: 14

Description:
  A large living form of raw elemental Earth, this creature can summon
  earthquakes and avalanches from its own Plane.

Commands:
  - summon earth:   Summons it to you         (costs 90 sp)
  - catt <monster>: Makes it attack <monster> (costs 10 sp)
  - cstop:          Makes it stop fighting    (costs 20 sp)
  - ban earth:      Banishes it               (costs 30 sp)
